sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server
    participant Database

    Client->>Server: Request data

    alt Data exists
        Server->>Database: Query
        Database-->>Server: Results
        Server-->>Client: Success response
    else No data
        Server-->>Client: Empty response
    end

    loop Health check
        Client->>Server: Ping
        Server-->>Client: Pong
    end
